3. IMPLEMENTATION SUMMARY
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  ParsedLogEvent:        eventId, snapshotId, serviceName, timestamp, severity, templateId, template,
                         rawMessage, parameters, traceId, spanId, threadName, loggerName,
                         exceptionClass, exceptionMessage, source (APP, ISTIO_ACCESS, ISTIO_ENVOY)
  DrainParser:           Fixed-depth tree, similarity threshold, preprocess/maskToken (<IP>, <UUID>, <NUM>, <PATH>),
                         thread-safe (read/write lock), updateTemplate, getClusters
  LogLineParser:         MICRONAUT_PATTERN, ISTIO_ACCESS_PATTERN, ISTIO_ENVOY_PATTERN,
                         RawLogLine, parseException (last match = root cause)
  TraceContextExtractor: W3C traceparent, B3 single header, TraceContext(traceId, spanId)
  LogParsingService:     parseSnapshotLogs → findLogFiles(*.log), readLines, lineParser.parse,
                         drainParser.parse, traceExtractor.extract, buildEvent, bulkIndex runtime-events,
                         putJson evidence/drain-clusters/{snapshotId}.json, inferServiceName
  LogParserConfig:       DrainParser bean (similarity-threshold, max-depth, max-children)

